videos.description: Joe Girard takes the ball the length of the court and hits a jumper from the free throw line to force overtime for Syracuse.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Girard hits a shot to force OT for Syracuse) 2020/03/07 ESHEETS

videos.headline: Girard hits a shot to force OT for Syracuse

videos.description: Isaiah Wong makes a move at the top of the key for Miami, gets free and launches a deep 3-pointer to put Miami up by five in overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Wong lines up a deep ball from atop the key and drills a 3 in OT) 2020/03/07 ESHEETS
